          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Respect for Native Americans in Professional Sports Act of 2015</strong></p> <p>This bill applies the antitrust laws to a professional sports league that uses, or promotes or allows a member team or franchisee to use or promote the use of, "Redskins" or "Redskin" in connection with such league or a team or franchise connected with such league.</p>]]></text>
